WEBVTT

00:04.003 --> 00:07.883
You wait 30 years for the woman you love,

00:07.883 --> 00:10.636
and finally you get her.

00:10.636 --> 00:12.930
And she slips through your fingers.

00:12.930 --> 00:14.181
I can help her.

00:15.849 --> 00:18.227
Marret's watching the baby?

00:18.227 --> 00:19.603
Wendell is 15, Mom.

00:19.603 --> 00:21.146
I want Wendell to be able

00:21.146 --> 00:22.397
to remember her when she's gone.

00:22.397 --> 00:23.398
I guess he could

00:23.398 --> 00:24.733
take a bus up there.

00:24.733 --> 00:26.944
You feel guilty about your mom,

00:26.944 --> 00:28.362
and your father,

00:28.362 --> 00:29.988
and your son, who barely has a father.

00:31.949 --> 00:33.700
Your right ear is ringing,

00:33.700 --> 00:36.078
so loud you can barely hear yourself think.

00:36.078 --> 00:38.330
Do you listen to 
loud music in your earbuds?

00:38.330 --> 00:39.915
It could just be tinnitus.

00:39.915 --> 00:42.459
- Do you hear it right now?
- Comes and goes.

00:42.459 --> 00:44.336
Used to bother me
when I was a teenager.

